<item>
            <title>[PIG-3858] PigLogger/PigStatusReporter is not set for fetch tasks</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-3858</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;PigLogger initialization is missing which leads to NPE if counters are accessed during a fetch tasks. Some queries to reproduce this issue:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;1.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;set opt.fetch &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;;
A = load ...
B = foreach A generate TOBAG(TOTUPLE(&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;null&lt;/span&gt;));
dump B;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;-&amp;gt; NPE when PigWarning.SKIP_UDF_CALL_FOR_NULL is incremented&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;2.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;set opt.fetch &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;;
set pig.udf.profile &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;;

A = load ...
B = foreach A generate [any UDF]
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;-&amp;gt; NPE when POUserFunc.INVOCATION_COUNTER is incremented&lt;/p&gt;</description>
